Package: twhotelpanel
Title: Build a Panel Dataset from Taiwan Tourist Hotel Monthly Reports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Liou", "Yuyou", email = "yuyou.liou@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Constructs a hotel-by-month panel dataset from the monthly
    operating-statistics reports of Taiwan's Tourism Administration (series
    "Tourist Hotel Operating Statistics", 觀光旅館營運統計). The package crawls
    the official file listing, downloads the monthly workbooks, parses the
    per-hotel operating tables, and assembles them into a tidy panel for
    empirical analysis. The source listing is available at
    <https://admin.taiwan.net.tw/businessinfo/FilePage?a=10425>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
